title: British soccer teams with most League Cup titles 2019
summary: This is a bar chart. It shows Number of titles for 23 number of Club Names.
The Number of titles is appeared to be the highest at Club Name Liverpool FC and lowest at Club Name Blackburn Rovers.
The highest Club Name Liverpool FC has 7.0 more Number of titles than the lowest Club Name Blackburn Rovers.
